At the close , the 100-quality stocks Composite Index lost 1.09 points to 832.80 , the all-share Emas Index dipped 0.58 of a point to 213.66 , the Industrial Index dropped 10.55 points to 1,422.22 , and the Second Board Index however added 7.05 points to 201.10 points . 
Gainers led losers by 424 to 310 while 115 counters were unchanged and 92 others untraded . 
The day 's total turnover decreased to 511.447 million shares valued at 1.350 billion ringgit -LBR- 355.263 million U.S. dollars -RBR- from Monday 's 539.912 million shares valued at 1.335 billion ringgit -LBR- 351.315 million U.S. dollars -RBR- .